            <p>GNEC Media is committed to protect and safeguard the privacy of its users. The content intends to let our users know and understand how we protect their privacy and all the personal and business information aptly while they use our services for their benefits. The policy applies to the entire network operated by GNEC Media.</p>

            <p>When the users register to gain access to the information, services, materials, or products provided by GNEC Media, they have to endow us with all the relevant personal data and other information related to business. The basic information like name, email address, business type, and some other personal information is collected during registration. Once you provide your personal and business information to GNEC media, it implies that you have given the right to publish this information to the relevant business and personal details all through the marketplace like catalogs, business directory, etc.</p>

            <p>When you are registering with us and providing your personal and business information, it remains safe and secure with GNEC Media, unless specified specifically. The promotional campaigns run by the sponsors under GNEC Media could collect the users’ information. We may share the data provided by the registered users only after notifying prior to the data collection or transfer. The users have the right to tell whether or not they want their information to pass or share with the sponsors of the promotions for participation.</p>

            <p>To improve the experience of the users with www.gnecmedia.com, we also collect some necessary usage statistics information like pages viewed, browser software, screen resolution, number of unique visitors, type of computer, and connectivity. This information helps us in enhancing the experience of users while browsing the website and utilizing its information and services.</p>

            <p>The personal, public, and business-related information collected by GNEC Media is solely to customize the experience of the users as per their requirements on our network of sites. It helps the registered users to gain access to maximum information and services that may help them grab better and improved business opportunities.</p>

            <p>GNEC Media displays advertisements based on the usage statistics of the website, and the trends visitors are showing which intends to provide services free of charge to the users. The personal and business information is served to the target advertisements via the website and customized emails. The buyers and sellers may start providing you the business inquiries which may or may not be of your interest. We are not responsible for the emails send to the listed members regarding business inquiries and do not hold any control over the matter.</p>

            <p>GNEC Media provide or disclose the personal and business information only after seeking the permission from the users, or give access only under exceptional circumstances wherein GNEC Media believes in good faith that the law requires it or as permitted in the terms and conditions of the site’s policy. Other than this, GNEC Media may also disclose the information in certain special cases in which sharing the personal and business details will become necessary to identify, contact or bring legal action against the user who is violating the Terms of Services of GNEC Media. If the user is causing interference either intentionally or unintentionally to the rights of property which GNEC Media or its network, the company is liable to maintain, the personal and business information may be shared.</p>

            <p>GNEC Media will send emails to its registered users from time to time regarding the products and services for an enhanced and improved experience. Apart from this, GNEC Media may also send emails regarding the products and services of the third party directly, which it feels is in interest with the information provided by the user. The third-party mails will be sent only by the GNEC Media or its agents working under confidential agreements.</p>

            <p>The users may edit the information provided in the profile anytime in GNEC Media by logging and sending a request through an email. It may take around 30 days to change the particulars as said by the user and appear online. The verification process and cache policies may take time, which may lead to a delay in updating the profile.</p>

            <p>The user may deactivate their account at www.gnecmedia.com or delete it permanently whenever they want. However, once deleted, the user will not be able to access the specific 'member-only' area of the network and draw its benefits. Our archive records will keep the residual information of the deleted users.</p>

            <p>GNEC Media is committed not to sell the personal information or the information provided by the users related to their business to anyone, if done, it will be only after seeking the permission from the concerned person. We always provide information in an aggregate form to the prospective advertisers or partners concerning the services or products used by the registered users on GNEC Media and its network. It will not include personally identifiable information.</p>

            <p>GNEC Media requests the users to always sign out of their GNEC Media account and close the browser window after accomplishing the work. It will make sure that no other person can access their personal details or the information related to their business and correspond. It becomes an essential step if you are using the computer in a public place or sharing the computer with others. We ensure taking all the vital steps to limit the commercial viability to secure the information of the users.</p>

            <p>Data transmission through the internet never holds of 100% guarantee of being secure. Although GNEC Media strives to secure the personal and business information of the users to its maximum, it cannot ensure the security of the information you provide to the GNEC Media completely, and you do so at your own risk. GNEC Media make full efforts to safeguard the information of users in its system as soon as it receives it.</p>

